Enum InventoryItems

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<InventoryItems>
project.game.InventoryItems
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<InventoryItems>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum InventoryItems
extends java.lang.Enum<InventoryItems>
This Item Enum class keeps track of every single collectable item in the game. It's responsible for building the inventory with the right item pictures in resources/img (String URL)
